choices.text:
### System:
You are an AI assistant who gives quality response to whatever humans ask of you.

### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for seven days.  My restrictions are dairy, milk-based yogurt, garlic, honey, almonds, almond butter, pistachios, and cashews

### Assistant:

Day 1:
Breakfast - Vegan protein smoothie bowl with mixed berries, banana, spinach, chia seeds, and coconut milk.
Lunch - Quinoa salad with roasted vegetables (zucchini, eggplant, bell peppers), cherry tomatoes, red onion, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and pepper.
Dinner - Vegan chickpea curry with sweet potato, cauliflower florets, green beans, coconut milk, turmeric, cumin, coriander, garam masala, and red chili flakes.
